reviews.content: The food was not that good! For the price you expect a higher quality.

When traveling in a strange city, sometimes you don’t know where to eat dinner. Lucky to find this restaurant (near my lives hotel). I ordered traditional Vietnamese spring rolls, the kind you have to make yourself, but I don't know how to …

The restaurant is located on the ground floor of the Cinestar cinema. There are many familiar dishes of the Central region, of course the price is higher than the sidewalk restaurants, but quite delicious. I ate Cao Lau noodles, thinking it …

I went to the restaurant at that time when there was a birthday party. The staff were very nice, although there was a party, they were not in a panic, I saw that all the staff were female, from the waiters to the managers and even …
Delicious food, a bit more expensive than outside but clean, staff is so cute, convenient if you want to watch movies here.
